'''天氣頻道'''（{{lang-en|'''The Weather Channel'''}}，簡稱{{lang|en|'''TWC'''}}）是{{link-en|艾伦传媒集团|Entertainment Studios}}子公司气象集团有限责任公司（Weather Group, LLC）所拥有的一個美国[[付费电视|付费电视]][[电视频道|频道]]<ref name="Entertainment Studios">{{Cite web|title=Byron Allen's Entertainment Studios Acquires The Weather Channel TV Network For $300 Million|url=https://deadline.com/2018/03/byron-allen-entertainment-studios-acquisition-the-weather-channel-tv-network-1202351426/|accessdate=March 22, 2018|author=Andreeva|date=March 22, 2018|first=Nellie|work=Deadline Hollywood|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120204124/https://deadline.com/2018/03/byron-allen-entertainment-studios-acquisition-the-weather-channel-tv-network-1202351426/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Byron Allen">{{Cite web|title=Byron Allen Acquires The Weather Group in $300 Million Deal|url=http://www.broadcastingcable.com/news/currency/byron-allen-acquires-weather-group-300-million-deal/172512|accessdate=March 22, 2018|author=Albiniak|date=March 22, 2018|first=Paige|work=Broadcasting & Cable|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180322203251/http://www.broadcastingcable.com/news/currency/byron-allen-acquires-weather-group-300-million-deal/172512|archivedate=2018-03-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该频道的总部位于美國[[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]][[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]。该频道于1982年5月2日开播，內容涵蓋[[天气预报|天气预报]]、與天气相关的新闻、分析、纪录片和娱乐节目<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nexttv.com/news/rfd-tv-connects-weather-channel-396626 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-21 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214222615/https://www.nexttv.com/news/rfd-tv-connects-weather-channel-396626 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2018年與The Future Group合作，使用[[混合實境|混合實境]]技術進行天氣預報<ref>{{cite news |last1=Martin |first1=Scott |title=暴風之眼：天氣頻道運用令人驚嘆的視覺效果來預測佛羅倫斯颶風的走向 |url=https://blogs.nvidia.com.tw/2018/09/14/in-the-eye-of-the-storm-the-weather-channel-forecasts-hurricane-florence-with-stunning-visuals/ |accessdate=2021-02-22 |work=NVIDIA 台灣官方部落格 |date=2018-09-14 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417084837/https://blogs.nvidia.com.tw/2018/09/14/in-the-eye-of-the-storm-the-weather-channel-forecasts-hurricane-florence-with-stunning-visuals/ }}</ref>，天氣頻道也因此獲得2019年[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]的「傑出科學、醫療或環境報道」獎<ref>{{cite news |title=The Weather Channel Wins Two Emmy Awards {{!}} The Weather Channel - Articles from The Weather Channel {{!}} weather.com |url=https://weather.com/news/news/2019-09-25-weather-channel-receives-two-emmy-awards |accessdate=2021-02-22 |work=The Weather Channel |date=2019-09-26 |language=en |archive-date=2020-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204032439/https://weather.com/news/news/2019-09-25-weather-channel-receives-two-emmy-awards |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

